{"type":"article_comment","id":220457,"parentType":"article","parentId":3868,"uid":28396,"contents":"本人当前：<br>\n政治立场坐标（左翼&lt;-&gt;右翼）1.8，<br>\n经济立场坐标（左翼&lt;-&gt;右翼）1.5，<br>\n文化立场坐标（保守&lt;-&gt;自由）1.6。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nX坐标反映政治观念，负值为左(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Authoritarianism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">独裁主义</a>)，正值为右(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Libertarianism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">自由意志主义</a>)。<br>\nY坐标反映经济观念，负值为左(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Communism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">共产主义</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collectivism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">集体主义</a>)，正值为右(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neoliberalism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新自由主义</a>)。<br>\nZ坐标反映社会文化观念，负值为<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conservatism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">保守主义</a>，正值为<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberalism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">自由主义</a>。","date":"2020-01-31","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}